Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
getCmdLogFileName(25.10)                              getCmdLogFileName(25.10)

Name
       getCmdLogFileName - Reports the name of the command log file

Syntax
       getCmdLogFileName [-help]

       Reports the name of the command log file.

       You can use the getCmdLogFileName command at any time during an Innovus
       session.

Parameters
       -help  Prints  a brief description of the getCmdLogFileName command us-
              age.

              For a detailed description of the command and all of its parame-
              ters, use the man command:

              man getCmdLogFileName.

Example
       The following command gives the command log file name:

       > getCmdLogFileName

       innovus.cmd3

